      <div class="p-4 border rounded"><strong>4. Submission</strong><p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">Follow-ups & updates.</p></div>
      <div class="p-4 border rounded"><strong>5. Approval</strong><p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">Card issuance & renewals.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <a href="../en/contact/" class="px-4 py-2 border rounded">Book a call</a>
    </div>
